<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7617058>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Habitus of Chrysolina orochi sp. nov., holotype male (TT0000010) (A – dorsal view, B – ventral view, C – lateral view), paratype female (TT0000156) (D – dorsal view, E – ventral view, F – lateral view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7617058/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7617060>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Growth stages of Chrysolina orochi sp. nov.:A – host plant, Artemisia capillaris Thunberg; B – eggs; C – first instar larva; D – third instar larva; E – last (fourth) instar larva; F – pupa; G – adult." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7617060/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7617068>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. External parts of Chrysolina orochi sp. nov. (TT0000022): A – head; B – pronotum, dorsal view; C – pronotum, ventral view; D – scutellum and elytron." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7617068/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7617072>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Microscopic surface structures of Chrysolina orochi sp. nov. (TT0000022):A – head; B – pronotum; C – elytron; D – metaventrite; E – sternite 1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7617072/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7617076>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Other external characters: A–E – Chrysolina orochi sp. nov.: A – right mandible; B – antenna; C – right hind wing; D–E – left maxillary palp (D – male, E – female). F – Ch. aeruginosa aeruginosa (Faldermann, 1835), right hind wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7617076/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7617074>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Male (TT-0000022) and female (TT-0000015) posterior margin of 7th sternite and all tarsi of Chrysolina orochi sp. nov.: A–B – posterior margin of 7th sternite (A – male, B – female); C, F – protarsus (C – male, F – female); D, G – mesotarsus (D – male, G – female); E, H – metatarsus (E – male, H – female)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7617074/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7617078>
    dc:description "Fig. 11. Genitalia of Chrysolina orochi sp. nov.: A–F – TT0000010; G–H – TT0000014. A – male 8th sternite; B–D – median lobe: B – apical portion in dorsal view; C – dorsal view; D – lateral view; E – spicule; F – tegmen; G – female 8th sternite; H – spermathecal organ." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7617078/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7617080>
    dc:description "Fig. 12. Habitus and external parts of 1st instar larva (A, B) and last instar larva (C–I) of Chrysolina orochi sp. nov.:A – habitus in lateral view; B – tibia and tarsungulus; C – habitus in lateral view; D – tibia and tarsungulus; E – head; F – mouthparts; G – mandible; H – labrum; I – tubercles and spiracle of 1st abdominal segment." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7617080/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7617082>
    dc:description "Fig. 13. External parts of larvae of Chrysolina orochi sp. nov.: A–B – setae of dorsum (A – 1st instar larva, B – last instar larva); C – apex of setae of 1st instar larva; D–E – tibia and tarsungulus (D – 1st instar larva, E – last instar larva)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7617082/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7617086>
    dc:description "Fig. 15. Pupa of Chrysolina orochi sp. nov.:A – dorsal view; B – ventral view; C – apex of sternite in dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7617086/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

